hopobject.body: I'd like to send this to manforce personalleasing gmbh If you didn't know, Isabel Marant is the coolest designer out there whose creations are less for the red carpet and more for every day. That's why they're so covetable - they immediately add a hit of cool girl chic to any look. Stylish celebrity ladies are as crazy for Marant as we are with Rosie Huntington-Whiteley, Abbey Crouch, Coleen Rooney, Kate Bosworth, Katie Holmes and Miranda Kerr all regularly seen in her designs.
